title: S1 SUP main (last season) LF Duo partner to climb with
body:
AS per title, I'm looking for someone to regularly duo with.

I was Silver 1 last season but couldn't break promo into gold, now it looks like I'm doing the same at the moment to get into Silver! If you're an ADC or mid main and keen to duo, hit me up.

IGN: I LICK BATTERIES
